<plot>ZONE is a trip through a person's mind. That trip shows all illusions, feelings, thoughts and reality that we might experience. The action goes from the outside to the inside of the person's head. The person gets involved into those illusions, and they become the part of reality. At the end, the madness in person's head stops and is described through the dark screen with silence, which will be disturbed with extremely fast change of images. That gives the impression that there is no end or escape.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?671963</url></doc>
